<p>I want <em>this</em> to ultimately set a <code>help</code> variable for me.</p>
<p>But if you try it now, <em>huge</em> error!</p>
<blockquote><p>The option "help" does not exist.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>That's no surprise: I just invented this option! But, we <em>can</em> make this work.</p>

    
